title: If the display property of an item is set to 'none', it doesn't take effect in new PDF emitter.
OB: When the display property of an item is set to 'none' in the new PDF emitter, it does not have any effect.
SR: To reproduce this issue: 1. Add a label. 2. Open the 'properties' view. 3. Set the sectionDisplay property of the label to 'none'.
